Y2  - 2024/03/26
N2  - ABSTRACT This paper reports the results of controlled experiments designed to test the Harris-Raviv generalization of the Vickrey theory of bidding in multiple unit discriminative auctions. The paper also discusses further development of the theory?in a way suggested by the experimental results?to include bidders with distinct risk preferences.
