T1  - Continuous Maturity Diversification of Default-Free Bond Portfolios and a Generalization of Efficient Diversification
AU  - HEANEY, W. JOHN
AU  - CHENG, PAO L.
Y1  - 1984/09/01
PY  - 1984
DA  - 1984/09/01
